Other videos:\\
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RCeH8xT2pGk\\
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6_wwORq2G4 (Portuguese)

===Commands===
* /itemstay - Create a new display.
* /itemstay list - Able to be used by anyone. Shows displays within 5 blocks of you.
* /itemstay delete [ID] - Lets you delete a display. Find the ID of the display by using the above command (/itemstay list).
* /itemstay reload - Reload the displays.
* /itemstay respawn - Reload the displays.

===Permissions===
* itemstay.admin - grants access to all commands
* itemstay.create - allows a player to create a display
* itemstay.delete - allows a player to delete displays
* ;itemstay.reload
:Lets a person use the '/itemstay reload' command.

===Support===
Leave a comment or make a support ticket for help with the plugin.\\
Plugin now cross-released at [[http://www.spigotmc.org/resources/itemstay.4403/|Spigot]].

===Compatibility===
The plugin should be compatible with pretty much any version you might be running, including 1.7.x, Spigot 1.8, 1.8.1, etc.

